Amazon Has A Private Food Brand That Just Launched 100 New Products For Fall

Lifestyle
Published Oct 19, 2022
By
Bethany Braun-Silva
Amazon

One of the best things about fall is all the food offerings. What's not to love when there's pumpkin spice everything, delicious turkey, and apples galore?

Fall is truly a season of food, and that's why we were so excited to discover Amazon's very own private food brand Aplenty, which just dropped over 100 new products perfect for your autumn festivities.

Amazon launched Aplenty last year, but it's currently making headlines for all the new items. We're talking Apple Pie Granola Clusters, Caramel Pumpkin Spice Popcorn, Pumpkin Spice Granola, Honey Crisp Apple Cider, Truffle Cheese Crisps, and more. Do we have your attention yet?

*Psst: if you choose to purchase an item from this post, LittleThings.com may receive a small cut. Each item and price is up to date at the time of publication; however, an item may be sold out or the price may be different at a later date.

Of course, it's never too late to stock up on things via Amazon, thanks to its fast shipping and extensive stock, but we would be remiss if we didn't tell you to hurry up and start adding these items to your cart (the Caramel Pumpkin Spice Popcorn is currently out of stock!).

We will be stocking up on the Chocolate Smores Bites, Truffle Oil & Mushrooms Thin and Crispy Pizza, and the 5-Cheese Mac & Cheese Bites to keep us cozy for fall.

If you're more into the holiday treat vibe, Aplenty will be releasing Sparkling Citrus Punch, Chocolate Peppermint Granola, Double Chocolate Truffle Hot Chocolate, White Chocolate Peppermint Popcorn, and more in the coming weeks.

Keep scrolling to check out some of our fall favorites from Amazon's Aplenty brand.

Aplenty Organic Sweet Potato Tortilla Chips

$3.00 from AmazonSHOP

Review: "I was surprised at how good these were! They hold up in dips, and are not too crackely. I found myself eating way past the recommended amount! (LOL)."

Aplenty Truffle Oil & Mushrooms Thin and Crispy Pizza

$7.00 from AmazonSHOP

Review: "This is my favorite frozen pizza--of ANY brand, and it is absolutely DELICIOUS!!! I keep one or two in the freezer at all times. I highly recommend it to anyone who hasn't tried it."

Aplenty Caramelized Onion & Feta Puffs

$4.00 from AmazonSHOP

Review: "Im kind of obsessed with all things feta cheese, so I knew Id love these and they didnt disappoint. Theyre good in a pinch when having company, especially with vegetarian friends although I tend to make them when I need an indulgent snack. Guilty! ."

Aplenty Coffee Crisp Dark Chocolate Bark

$4.00 from AmazonSHOP

Review: "Love this coffee chocolate. I usually dont like dark chocolate too much but this stuff is soooo good. If you love coffee and chocolate it doesnt disappoint!"
